data.title: 以 1 到 3 分钟谈论以下主题
data.content: What is the greatest accomplishment of your life? How did you achieve it?
data.answer: My greatest achievement is that I have managed to lose weight. When I was young, I was much overweight because of my gluttony, even a little exercise would make me very tired, it was very unhealthy. Then I determined to enhance my health and lose weight, so I started to control my diet and exercise regularly, after almost 1 year of hard work, I finally regained my normal weight and rewarded myself with a stronger body, and my exercise habits had been maintained to this day so that I can live a regular life.
